# Modern Personal Portfolio Website

A clean, minimal, professional portfolio website featuring glassmorphism UI, dark/light mode toggle, smooth animations, and fully responsive design.

## Features
✅ **Glassmorphism Design** - Modern frosted glass effects  
✅ **Dark/Light Mode** - Toggle with localStorage persistence  
✅ **Smooth Animations** - Scroll reveal, typing effect, hover animations  
✅ **Fully Responsive** - Mobile-first design  
✅ **Interactive Elements** - Form validation, progress bars, scroll-to-top  
✅ **Contact Form** - Client-side validation  
✅ **Projects Showcase** - Grid layout with hover effects  

## Quick Start
1. Open `index.html` in your browser
2. Toggle dark/light mode (top-right corner)
3. Scroll to see animations in action
4. Test the contact form

## Customization
- Replace placeholder images with your project screenshots
- Update personal info in HTML sections
- Modify skills progress bars data-width values (0-100)
- Update social links, contact info, project links
- Customize colors in `style.css` gradient variables

## Tech Stack
```
HTML5 | CSS3 (Flexbox/Grid) | Vanilla JavaScript
Font Awesome Icons | LocalStorage | Intersection Observer API
```

## Deployment
Ready to deploy on:
- **Vercel** (drag & drop folder)
- **Netlify** (drag & drop)
- **GitHub Pages**
- Any static hosting service

## File Structure
```
portfolio-website/
├── index.html      # Main structure & content
├── style.css       # Glassmorphism styling & animations
└── script.js       # Interactive features & functionality
```

**Live Demo:** Open `index.html` or deploy to Vercel/Netlify
